          paid work per year to each rural household, boosting employment and creating community
          assets&#8203;:contentReference[oaicite:2]{index=2}.</li>
        <li><strong>PMAY-G:</strong> The Pradhan Mantri Awaas Yojana ‚Äì Gramin is a flagship rural housing scheme aimed
