          rural poor&#8203;:contentReference[oaicite:3]{index=3}.</li>
        <li><strong>PMFBY:</strong> The Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojana offers comprehensive crop insurance for
          farmers‚Äô yields. It reduces the financial burden on farmers by covering crop losses and ensuring timely claim
          settlements&#8203;:contentReference[oaicite:4]{index=4}.</li>
        <li><strong>PMUY:</strong> The Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala Yojana provides free or subsidized LPG connections to
          women from Below Poverty Line families, improving health and safety by giving access to clean cooking
          fuel&#8203;:contentReference[oaicite:5]{index=5}.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

